    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? Mindspace Business Parks REIT in Bengaluru offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Mindspace Business Parks REIT:\nMindspace Business Parks REIT is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mindspace Business Parks REIT!",
